# PandaralÂ·lel

[![PyPI version fury.io](https://badge.fury.io/py/pandarallel.svg)](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pandarallel/)
[![PyPI license](https://img.shields.io/pypi/l/pandarallel.svg)](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pandarallel/)
